rce/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The fast-food chain's sponsorship deal with the Olympics has since expired.\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1675, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This year, though, Amandine Chaignot, which has two Michelin stars - Alexandre Mazzia and Akrame Benallal - are among the leading French chefs to inspire the new offerings.\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1696, \"end\": 1713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amandine_Chaignot\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amandine Chaignot\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amandine_Chaignot\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amandine_Chaignot\"}, {\"begin\": 1729, \"end\": 1737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2762324741988575e-16, \"text\": \"Michelin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\"}, {\"begin\": 1807, \"end\": 1813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.987755144793661, \"rank\": 0.012265065846751806, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"One very specific French feature that we have set up at the main village, also close to the bakery, is our Michelin starred chef kitchen, so twice per day, the athletes can also go there and really discover very high level, high profile French cuisine cooked on site by our Michelin star chefs,\\\" W\\u00fcrz added.\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 2159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1870, \"end\": 1876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.987755144793661, \"rank\": 0.012265065846751806, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org